*Teltoli snorts through her throat and then looks across, seeing another raptor bot talk into her com. Had to be her. She shoots a blast at a Predacon standing in her way and makes her way over to the raptor*

"I presume you're a Maximal, and have obviously been on this world longer than I. Mind if tag along? And what was that boom?"

*Hoping she doesn't seem annoying with all the questions, she stands and ducks another blast. Far out, where were all those blasts coming from! She mentally corrects herself, well duh Teltoli..*

* Iron Raptor snarled as she deactivated her com-link only to have it come 
alive with a new voice, it had to be that bot that she had tried to contact.
She reopened her link and spoke into it...*

" I am at coordinates 12.773, just across the field from you. It's nice to 
meet you Teltoli."

* She then looked over and saw that the fuzor was having a little trouble of 
her own, she hated to say it but...*

" And welcome...to the Beast Wars!"
